{"tid":888914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"壹仔: 曾性侵香港女星藍潔瑛","createTime":"2018-11-04T07:17:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T07:20:21.000Z","uid":28181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"46f64916233148de8a0208166d714e014bc0d9d4","tid":888914,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T07:17:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FY8aPAm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFY8aPAm.jpg&h=dab61862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nextmag.com.tw/realtimenews/news/451810?fbclid=IwAR3eO20VJvg-IhmfzhcEShKWXc4a7-wqnjVR8SKau309spyrx2nHV8B5zSI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nextmag.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Fnews%2F451810%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3eO20VJvg-IhmfzhcEShKWXc4a7-wqnjVR8SKau309spyrx2nHV8B5zSI&d=8dA%2FicDEPNKOZgrjHyrZlv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=986342e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nextmag.com.tw/realtimenews/news/451810?fbclid=IwAR3eO20VJvg-IhmfzhcEShKWXc4a7-wqnjVR8SKau309spyrx2nHV8B5zSI</a>"},{"pid":"25aeee06225999389cb4c3f1aede07be624eff4b","tid":888914,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T07:19:08.000Z","msg":"香港《蘋果日報》報導，港星藝人藍潔瑛，今天3日凌晨驚傳暴斃，享年55歲。一名雷姓女子於周六凌晨零時許報警，指藍姓女友人，住家沒有人應門，房子還出現異味及噪音。《蘋果日報》記者到場時，發現警方已將藍潔瑛住家封鎖，屋內仍飄出惡臭。<br />\n<br />\n消防破門後，發現女屋主倒臥地上，證實死亡。警方初步調查，沒有他殺等可疑跡象，把案件列為「發現屍體」處理，死因有待驗屍後確認。鄰居透露，死者就是藍潔瑛。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n貌美封靚絕五台山<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藍潔瑛早期演出多部港劇，美貌曾獲「靚絕五台山」封號，與梅艷芳、張曼玉齊名。藍潔瑛1992年主演TVB 25周年台慶經典大戲《大時代》，憑「羅慧玲」一角再獲觀眾青睞，還獲選十大電視藝人。撰文：宋志民　圖片：翻攝網路）<br />\n<br />\n昔日性侵風波新聞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nextmag.com.tw/realtimenews/news/379114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nextmag.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Fnews%2F379114&d=8dA%2FicDEPNKOZgrjHyrZlv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=05e46791\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nextmag.com.tw/realtimenews/news/379114</a>"},{"pid":"229076509f985870f740bd5eb6c47da5a5cbd752","tid":888914,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T07:20:12.000Z","msg":"起個題都賤過人~"},{"pid":"5da7d691f9543243e0694f85a8337d94802e71ec","tid":888914,"uid":72415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T07:20:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}